OL,7,FA 12-year-old boy is in a critical
OL,8,Fcondition after being hit by
OL,9,Flightning at a school football
OL,10,Ftournament during storms.
OL,12,FIt happened at about 5.15pm on Monday
OL,13,Fduring a tournament taking place at
OL,14,FThe Sele School in Hertford.
OL,16,FThe tournament had been called off
OL,17,Fdue to the weather and the teams were
OL,18,Fleaving the pitch when the lightning
OL,19,Fbolt hit the boy, the school's
OL,20,Fheadteacher told ITV News Anglia.
